name: [Sign-in User][Project][.COM]Place order using SHIP TO ME with Master Credit Card

steps.name: Given User will open website
When User accept cookies
When the user provides valid credentials to sign in
When User should click in sigin button
When User will click on cart button
Then User Will Clear the Cart
When User Should click on Main Menu Button
When User has to click on projects and navigate to project homepage
When User scroll down into page and click on searchbox
When the user enters modernArt project in the search bar
When User will select project and click on that project
When User will navigate to PDP Page and click on Add All Items to cart
When User will click on cart button
When User will select ship to me as the shipping method
When User should click on checkout button
When User will click on payment and order review button
When User will add the Card Details like Name on Card,Card Number,Expiration Date,CVV
When User will click on Place order button
When User will redirected to Order Confirmation Page
When User should find Order confirmation with order number
